data.name: PortNameB.ToolTip
data.value: Port name. The name is red if it's already in use by other device. Enter '-' to reset the name to the default.

data.name: PortNameA.ToolTip
data.value: Port name. The name is red if it's already in use by other device. Enter '-' to reset the name to the default.

data.name: UsePortsClassB.ToolTip
data.value: Allow Ports class installer to set the real port name. The Ports class installer selects the COM port number and sets the real port name to COM<n>, where <n> is the selected port number. Thereafter you will be able to change port number.

data.name: UsePortsClassA.ToolTip
data.value: Allow Ports class installer to set the real port name. The Ports class installer selects the COM port number and sets the real port name to COM<n>, where <n> is the selected port number. Thereafter you will be able to change port number.

data.name: picturePinMap.ToolTip
data.value: One green pin can be wired to one red pin. One red pin can be wired to multiple green pins. Double click a green pin to add/remove inverter.

data.name: EmuBrB.ToolTip
data.value: Enable/disable baud rate emulation in the direction to the paired port.

data.name: PlugInModeB.ToolTip
data.value: Enable/disable plug-in mode. The plug-in mode port is hidden and can't be open if the paired port is not open.

data.name: ExclusiveModeB.ToolTip
data.value: Enable/disable exclusive mode. The exclusive mode port is hidden if it is open.

data.name: ExclusiveModeA.ToolTip
data.value: Enable/disable exclusive mode. The exclusive mode port is hidden if it is open.

data.name: PlugInModeA.ToolTip
data.value: Enable/disable plug-in mode. The plug-in mode port is hidden and can't be open if the paired port is not open.

data.name: EmuBrA.ToolTip
data.value: Enable/disable baud rate emulation in the direction to the paired port.

data.name: HiddenModeA.ToolTip
data.value: Enable/disable hidden mode. The hidden mode port is hidden as it is possible for port enumerators.

data.name: HiddenModeB.ToolTip
data.value: Enable/disable hidden mode. The hidden mode port is hidden as it is possible for port enumerators.

data.name: pinNameA_OPEN.ToolTip
data.value: OPEN - logical ON if the port is open.

data.name: pinNameB_OPEN.ToolTip
data.value: OPEN - logical ON if the port is open.

data.name: buttonAddPair.ToolTip
data.value: Add a new port pair with default parameters.

data.name: buttonApply.ToolTip
data.value: Apply the changed parameters (highlighted with blue color).

data.name: buttonReset.ToolTip
data.value: Reload the current parameters and redraw the form.
